## Reflection

### Your Digital Habit

Take a few minutes to connect today's lesson with the systems you built in Module 2.

1. **Digital Habit Piling:** Identify one existing daily routine (e.g., "closing my laptop at the end of the session").
2. **Add a 2-Minute Digital Rule:** Attach a new digital organization or security habit to it. For example, "Before I close my laptop, I will spend 2 minutes backing up my project files to secure cloud storage to protect against data loss and ransomware".
3. **Share with your Habit Buddy:** Briefly explain to your accountability partner how you plan to protect your passwords and respect data privacy this week.

